review: **** ******* * **** **** **** ******* She is very experienced and communicates very clearly and kindly! Dr Sheetal is an excellent dentist! She takes her time with every patient and is highly considerate of your comfort and well-being. No sign of sensitivity or issues after my cavity fillings! Which I usually have problems with. Dentist appointments never ran as smoothly as this!
